CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 15, 1941 reads: " Margaret Lunette Lavelle celebrated her eighteenth birthday with a party at the home of her sister Mrs. Malvin R. Goode in Anaheim street. Margaret lives with her mother, Mrs. Mary Lavelle, and brothers, the well known Frank and Robert Lavelle of 8103 Perchmont street. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Margaret Lunette Lavelle, wearing light colored dress with lace and sheer overlay, and flower in hair, seated on chair in interior with ornate mirror on wall with floral wallpaper
